        	<h2>Vision for the Model</h2>
        </div>
    	<div class="about-box-right">
        	<p>A consumer outreach initiative that will allow them to book a diagnostics test or a health check-up by just scanning a QR code from their nearby pharmacies/chemists. A hassle free way for consumers to book FREE Home Collection slots and strong customer relationship bonding for pharmacists as well. <span style="color:#00ad4d; font-weight:900;">#PharmacyBhiDiagnosticsBhi</span></p>
        </div> 
        </div>
